{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 59,
  "title": "第五十九章（長生）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "治人事天 莫若嗇"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯嗇 是以蚤服 蚤服是謂重積德 重積德則无不克 无不克則莫知亓極 莫知亓極 可以有國 有國之母 可以長久"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂深根固柢 長生久視之道也"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 2,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "事，用也。當用天道，順四時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "嗇，愛惜也。治國者當愛民財，不為奢泰。治身者當愛精氣，不為放逸。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "早，先也。服，得也。夫獨愛民財，愛精氣，則能先得天道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先得天道，是謂重積德於己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "剋，勝也。重積德於己，則無不勝。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無不剋勝，則莫有知己德之窮極也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 34,
          "end": 35
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "莫知己德者有極，則可以有社稷，為民致福。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "國身同也。母，道也。人能保身中之道，使精氣不勞，五神不苦，則可以長久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 53
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能以氣為根，以精為蒂，如樹根不深則拔，蒂不堅則落。言當深藏其氣，固守其精，使無漏洩。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "深根固蒂者，乃長生久視之道。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "莫若，猶莫過也。嗇，農夫，農人之治田務，去其殊類，歸於齊一也。全其自然，不急其荒病，除其所以荒病，上承天命，下綏百姓，莫過於此。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "早服，常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯重積德，不欲銳速，然後乃能使早服其常，故曰早服謂之重積德者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道無窮也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 34,
          "end": 35
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以有窮而莅國，非能有國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "國之所以安謂之母，重積德是唯圖其根，然後營末，乃得其終也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
